## PLAYVISION REPORTER – COMPLETE PRODUCT DOCUMENTATION

1. INTRODUCTION
   PlayVision Reporter is a fully custom-built reporting framework designed exclusively for Playwright test automation.
   The goal is to replace Allure, Extent, and Playwright HTML Reporter with a faster, cleaner, and AI-powered reporting engine.
   The tool generates visually rich HTML reports, supports test artifacts, and provides intelligent error insights without external services.

This reporter is packaged as an independent NPM library and can be published under your name.

---

2. CORE OBJECTIVES

* Provide a lightweight HTML reporting engine
* Capture screenshots, videos, traces, console logs
* Track step execution flow
* Offer intelligent AI error analysis
* Work flawlessly with Playwright parallel execution
* No external servers, dashboards, or integrations
* Extremely fast and easy to install
* Zero dependencies on Allure or other frameworks

