9. PLAYWRIGHT CONFIGURATION

Modify playwright.config.js:

reporter: [
["list"],
["playvision", {
outputFolder: "playvision-report",
screenshots: true,
videos: "retain-on-failure",
aiAnalysis: true
}]
];

